              <div class="shortcut-row"><span class="shortcut-desc">Save file edit</span>   <span class="shortcut-keys"><kbd>&#8984;</kbd><kbd>S</kbd><span style="opacity:.6;padding:0 3px">/</span><kbd>&#8984;</kbd><kbd>&#8679;</kbd><kbd>S</kbd></span></div>
